Package simulation

  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    ATMPanel
    The GUI panel that simulates the ATM itself
    BillsPanel
    The GUI panel that allows the operator to enter the number of bills in the ATM at startup
    CardPanel
    The GUI panel that simulates the reading of the ATM card's magnetic stripe by asking the user to enter the number
    GUI
    The GUI for the ATM simulation
    LogPanel
    The GUI panel that displays the ATM's internal log
    SimCardReader
    Simulate the card reader
    SimCashDispenser
    Simulate the cash dispenser
    SimDisplay
    Simulate the display portion of the customer console
    SimEnvelopeAcceptor
    Simulate the envelope acceptor
    SimKeyboard
    Simulate the keyboard portion of the customer console
    SimOperatorPanel
    Simulate the operator panel
    SimReceiptPrinter
    Simulate the receipt printer
    SimulatedBank
    Simulation of the bank.
    Simulation
    Simulation of the physical components of the ATM, including its network connection to the bank.
